SDMProjectID: your project id shown in the SDM console
GCPProjectID: your project id shown in the GCP console
OAuthClientID: oauth client id created in GCP and set in SDM console
OAuthClientSecret: oauth client secret created in GCP
AccessToken: oauth access token obtained in the initial token request
RefreshToken: oauth refresh token obtained in the initial token request
ServiceAccountKey: credential of the GCP service account
